3
00:00:30,010 --> 00:00:33,020
Welcome to Last Week Tonight.

4
00:00:33,060 --> 00:00:36,000
I'm John Oliver.
Thank you for joining us.

5
00:00:36,020 --> 00:00:39,100
A quick recap of the week.
We begin in Washington,

6
00:00:39,120 --> 00:00:43,120
where Bill Barr failed to turn up
to a congressional hearing,

7
00:00:43,140 --> 00:00:46,210
an act that prompted
this prop comedy.

8
00:00:47,170 --> 00:00:51,180
Congressman Steve Cohen munched
on a bucket of fried chicken

9
00:00:51,210 --> 00:00:55,200
and flaunted a ceramic chicken
to drive his point home.

10
00:00:56,030 --> 00:00:58,120
What is the message
you're trying to send?

11
00:00:58,140 --> 00:01:00,080
Bill Barr is a chicken.

12
00:01:00,440 --> 00:01:05,410
Yeah, we get it.
You've made that painfully obvious.

13
00:01:06,330 --> 00:01:09,470
