to bring 'em down!

133
00:08:09,490 --> 00:08:14,370
I get angrier than a junkyard dog!
I stand tough and carry a big hammer.

134
00:08:14,390 --> 00:08:15,450
I growl and bark.

135
00:08:15,470 --> 00:08:17,430
- Wake up!
- It's Hammer-time!

136
00:08:17,450 --> 00:08:19,440
I'm Jim Adler,
the Texas Hammer.

137
