139
00:08:23,400 --> 00:08:24,440
Double down.

140
00:08:24,460 --> 00:08:26,520
Double the hammers,
double the justice.

141
00:08:26,550 --> 00:08:30,430
I fight for your medical bills,
paychecks, pain and suffering.

142
00:08:30,450 --> 00:08:33,500
- Jim Adler, Texas Hammer.
